And in 372 in your hymnal there,

00:02:04.239 --> 00:02:08.779
the songwriter Philip P. Bliss wrote these amazing words,

00:02:08.779 --> 00:02:12.080
obviously penned as he was meditating

00:02:12.080 --> 00:02:14.240
upon the truth of God's word.

00:02:14.240 --> 00:02:18.039
I would assume that the passage before us this morning

00:02:18.039 --> 00:02:21.220
