00:02:32.339 --> 00:02:36.979
Notice, free from the law, O happy condition,

00:02:36.979 --> 00:02:41.979
Jesus hath bled and there is remission.

00:02:42.220 --> 00:02:46.179
Cursed by the law and bruised by the fall,

00:02:46.179 --> 00:02:50.160
