00:03:03.240 --> 00:03:08.240
It continues, Jesus provides a perfect salvation.

00:03:08.839 --> 00:03:12.639
Come unto me, O hear his sweet call.

00:03:12.639 --> 00:03:17.160
Come and he saves us once for all.

00:03:17.160 --> 00:03:20.220
Children of God, O glorious calling,

00:03:20.220 --> 00:03:23.800
surely his grace will keep us from falling.

00:03:23.800 --> 00:03:26.759
Passing from death to life at his call,

00:03:26.759 --> 00:03:30.520
blessed salvation once for all.

00:03:30.520 --> 00:03:34.039
The chorus says, once for all, O sinner, receive it.

00:03:34.039 --> 00:03:37.199
Once for all, O brother, believe it.

00:03:37.199 --> 00:03:40.279
Cling to the cross, the burden will fall.

00:03:40.279 --> 00:03:44.940
Christ hath redeemed us once for all.

00:03:44.940 --> 00:03:48.619
I love the great hymns and how they minister to our heart

00:03:48.619 --> 00:03:51.979
and how they remind us of biblical teaching,

00:03:51.979 --> 00:03:53.979
biblical truth.

00:03:53.979 --> 00:03:56.940
The message in the book of Hebrews is a message

00:03:56.940 --> 00:03:59.059
