00:07:19.299 --> 00:07:22.500
should have had no more conscience of sins.

00:07:22.500 --> 00:07:24.100
You know what he's saying in verse number two?

00:07:24.100 --> 00:07:26.980
If the law could satisfy,

00:07:26.980 --> 00:07:31.339
if those Old Testament sacrifices could satisfy,

00:07:31.339 --> 00:07:35.140
