00:07:38.059 --> 00:07:42.140
it would have satisfied the demands of our holy God.

00:07:42.140 --> 00:07:44.700
So he says, for then would they not have ceased

00:07:44.700 --> 00:07:45.540
to be offered.

00:07:45.540 --> 00:07:46.380
No, they didn't cease.

00:07:46.380 --> 00:07:48.540
In fact, he continues in verse three,

00:07:48.540 --> 00:07:51.899
