00:07:51.899 --> 00:07:56.899
there is a remembrance again made of sins every year.

00:07:57.260 --> 00:07:59.859
Now, as you begin reading in Hebrews chapter number nine,

00:07:59.859 --> 00:08:04.660
specifically what's in view is the day of atonement.

00:08:04.660 --> 00:08:06.820
And it was on that particular day,

00:08:06.820 --> 00:08:09.820
that day of atonement that the high priest

00:08:09.820 --> 00:08:12.940
and the high priest alone with blood

00:08:12.940 --> 00:08:15.299
would enter into the holy of holies.

00:08:15.299 --> 00:08:17.739
It was the only time in the calendar year

00:08:17.739 --> 00:08:20.899
