00:08:42.299 --> 00:08:45.419
the Lord Jesus Christ, as he's introduced to us

00:08:45.419 --> 00:08:47.739
here in the book of Hebrews in that way,

00:08:47.739 --> 00:08:52.219
we find that he entered in not for his own sin,

00:08:52.219 --> 00:08:54.099
