00:09:53.979 --> 00:09:58.140
that God gives us here in Hebrews chapter number 10.

00:09:58.140 --> 00:09:59.940
We find that this sacrifice.

00:09:59.940 --> 00:10:04.940
that was made once for all, one sacrifice as it says there

00:10:05.040 --> 00:10:08.040
in verse number 12, after he made one,

00:10:08.040 --> 00:10:13.040
