00:10:33.240 --> 00:10:35.920
The reality is in chapter nine in verse number 22,

00:10:35.920 --> 00:10:39.440
we read this wonderful promise or reality truth

00:10:39.440 --> 00:10:42.120
that says in almost all things are by the law purged

00:10:42.120 --> 00:10:47.120
with blood and without shedding of blood is no remission.

00:10:50.020 --> 00:10:51.460
Now think about this with me,

00:10:51.460 --> 00:10:54.840
all of that Old Testament sacrificial system

00:10:54.840 --> 00:10:58.280
as they would come daily and making those sacrifices

00:10:58.280 --> 00:11:01.820
