00:11:01.820 --> 00:11:03.700
and all that would take place,

00:11:03.700 --> 00:11:08.540
it was a picture of Jesus Christ, the Lamb of God

00:11:08.540 --> 00:11:12.540
who would come as we read here in once for all,

00:11:12.540 --> 00:11:16.300
