00:11:16.300 --> 00:11:19.139
It was a picture as they would look forward

00:11:19.139 --> 00:11:24.139
to Jesus coming to this earth and dying upon the cross,

00:11:24.440 --> 00:11:27.040
of course, then rising from the dead,

00:11:27.040 --> 00:11:30.220
conquering sin, death and the grave.

00:11:30.220 --> 00:11:32.560
We find that in verse 18 of chapter 10,

00:11:32.560 --> 00:11:35.440
