00:11:52.500 --> 00:11:55.279
Now understand this, it's not letting them go

00:11:55.279 --> 00:11:58.400
as in God turns a blind eye.

00:11:58.400 --> 00:12:02.000
No, that's not justice, amen.

00:12:02.000 --> 00:12:06.760
Justice demands that sin be paid for.

00:12:06.760 --> 00:12:09.960
Your sin and my sin and the sin of the world

00:12:09.960 --> 00:12:11.279
