00:12:11.279 --> 00:12:13.919
The Bible says that that sin,

00:12:13.919 --> 00:12:15.960
it tells us the penalty of sin is what?

00:12:15.960 --> 00:12:17.400
It's death.

00:12:17.400 --> 00:12:21.400
